## Development

### Database

```bash
# Start PostgreSQL
docker compose up -d db

# Connect to database
docker compose exec db psql -U postgres -d app
```

### Testing

```bash
# All tests
./gradlew test

# With coverage
./gradlew test jacocoTestReport

# Specific test class
./gradlew test --tests "UserServiceTest"
```

## Docker

```bash
# Build and run all services
docker compose up -d

